text: Shanaka Sampath (born 17 June 1991) is a Sri Lankan cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Kalutara Town Club in the 2017–18 SLC Twenty20 Tournament on 27 February 2018. He made his List A debut for Kalutara Town Club in the 2017–18 Premier Limited Overs Tournament on 18 March 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan cricketers Category:Kalutara Town Club cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
